snippet.title: Eternal Hope - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
AVAILABLE NOW: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1162280/Eternal_Hope/ 

Eternal Hope, a fantasy adventure game that tells the story of Ti’bi – a boy who must embark on a journey of love and hope to find his beloved’s soul.

Website: https://www.eternalhopegame.com
Discord: http://discord.gg/uSTkerV
Twitter: https://twitter.com/doublehitgames
